lead_paragraph: - Gaston Ramirez scored a magnificent solo goal to set Middlesbrough on their way to their first home win of the Premier League season and bring an end to Bournemouth's fine recent run on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Ramirez Tour De Force Sets Boro on Way to Much-Needed Win
